## CI gating philosophy

| Gate | Layer | Action |
|---|---|---|
| Block on red | unit + integration + critical-path E2E | merge blocked |
| Soft-block | mutation score regression > {{mutDelta}} | warn, require justification |
| Soft-block | perf budget regression > {{perfDelta}}% | warn, require justification |
| Inform-only | a11y score, visual diff, full-suite mutation | annotate PR, don't block |
| Nightly only | sandbox payments, full mutation, k6 load | non-blocking, alert on regression |

